<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śakavarṣaṁbulu 1286 gunēṁṭṭi caitra śuddha 10 guruvārāna
<lb n="2"/>kṣīrārāmīśvaraśrīmahādēvarala saryyalu sēyiṁpeḍi
<lb n="3"/>bōyu jītanaku kōnabhīmavallabharājula Ānatini ci
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṁgarāju nāganabōyuṁḍu dēvara bhaṁḍārāna kānikāpeṭṭu
<lb n="5"/>gadyalu 10 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> I bōyiniki kṣētramu tūrppuna polāna kasi
<lb n="6" break="no"/>miseṟvu vuttarāna kha 1 na 10 graggipartti tūrppuna na 3
<lb n="7"/>koḍapalāmu seṟupu dakṣaṇāna Ayipakōḍu na 7
<lb n="8"/>peddāva<unclear>rā</unclear>na Ayipasēnu sariya tūrppu na 3 bera
<lb n="9" break="no"/>si kha 2 na 3 viṁdhyavāsiguḍi Utta<unclear>raṁ</unclear> Ilupaṭṭu na
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ganabōyuṁḍu Ācaryya Ejñēśvarabhaṭōpādhyala
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ku peṭṭina reṁḍu māḍalunu dēvara bhaṁḍārānaka Isiri <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
<lb n="12"/>berasi ga 12 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> svadataṁ paradataṁ vā yō harēti vasuṁdha
<lb n="14" break="no"/>raḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śaṣṭirvvarṣasahasrāṇi viṣṭāyāṁ jāyatē krimiḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

